  "description": "Simple mod to add more vanilla-like items and tools to minecraft",
  "body": "<p style=\"padding-left: 420px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/K8klbj2.png\" alt=\"Unadded Expansion\" width=\"607\" height=\"341\" /></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 420px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 420px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\"><a title=\"Fabric\" href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fabric-api\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ol1Tcf8.png\" alt=\"Fabric API\" width=\"131\" height=\"44\" /></a></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Features</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'andale mono', monospace; font-size: 12px; color: #808000;\">+ Deepslate Items (Stone items with more durability and less Attack Speed)</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: 'andale mono', monospace; color: #808000;\">+ Amethyst Items</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: 'andale mono', monospace; color: #808000;\">+ Emerald Items (You can only get this items trading with a villager, the items naturally has Mending and some cases have Fortune V and Looting V)</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: 'andale mono', monospace; color: #808000;\">+ Obsidian Armor (10 Knockback Resistance)</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: 'andale mono', monospace; color: #808000;\">+ Dragon Scale Items (Dragon Scale Pickaxe can break End Portal Frame and End Portal Block)</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: 'andale mono', monospace; color: #808000;\">+ End Respawn Anchor</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'andale mono', monospace; color: #993300;\">* Obsidian, Cry Obsidian and End Portal Frame don't burn anymore</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Forge port?</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp; 1.19 Soon</p>\n<p>&nbsp; 1.18.2 Maybe</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Backport?</p>\n<p>&nbsp; 1.17.1 Maybe</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10px;\">WIP: Bugs are expected</span></p>",
